data.description:
NEW Roof, NEW Exterior Paint, and New Deck Finishes!
Welcome to your New Home located on a Corner Lot just outside of the Poudre Pond Trails! One of the few homes featuring a 3-CAR Garage, a Huge, newly rebuilt deck for All your grilling needs, and an unfinished basement waiting for your own Inspiration! Whatever you're looking for- you'll find peace of mind in this charming home. This location is Ideal for those who want the Convenience of Greeley but without the noise. And let's not forget the 3-car garage, completely setup with 220 Volt just waiting for your toys! The home just had its roof replaced, the exterior repainted, and the deck rebuilt. The basement is Unfinished, leaving an opening for a savvy investor to go ahead and add more finished space of their own! To make it that much better- this basement is Ready for an additional bathroom. And if you like beautiful trails and some awesome fishing - Poudre Ponds is 
stocked for you, just 1.1 miles away!
More Photos to Come!
OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, October 10th!!!
Video Walkthrough Available- https://youtu.be/FgL70sGxZqE?si=CQK3kLnovlL2r1jL
